<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="21Feb1938"><font color="red">21 February 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Geoffrey Faber to Paul L&eacute;on): Thank you for your letter of the 17th. I am very sorry to hear that Mr Joyce&apos;s eyesight has been suffering from the strain of his work. </div>
